  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_135",
    "english": "Among the orcs of the Demon Realm, these have learned the skills to use magic. They use spells that kill the pain, allowing others to continue with the battle. Even if they know how to use magic, an orc is an orc, and they favor smacking the enemy with their staff rather than using an attack spell.",
